Tasks:
load_accounts
clear_accounts
send_activate_mail

[load_accounts]
1. put file to root directory of project, name it 'accounts.txt'
2. format of the accounts.txt file:
员工ID_中文名_英文名
3. run task: rake load_accounts

[clear_accounts]
this will delete all the accounts in database.

[send_activate_mail]
this will find all inactive accounts and send activate mail to each of them.
before run this task, please ensure mail settings in environment.rb is correct.